msgid "pre-commit テンプレートを更新（mypy 対応と default Python 指定）"
msgstr ""
"Updated pre-commit template (mypy compatible and default Python specified)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-27-pre-commit-template-update-mypy.rst:9
msgid "以前紹介した pre-commit のテンプレートに対し、以下のアップデートを行った。"
msgstr ""
"The following updates have been made to the pre-commit template introduced "
"previously."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-27-pre-commit-template-update-mypy.rst:11
msgid ":doc:`pre-commit テンプレート <2025-05-17-pre-commit-template>` の内容を更新。"
msgstr ":doc:`pre-commit テンプレート <2025-05-17-pre-commit-template>` の内容を更新。"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-27-pre-commit-template-update-mypy.rst:14
msgid "主な変更点"
msgstr "Main changes"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-27-pre-commit-template-update-mypy.rst:16
msgid "default_language_version の追加"
msgstr "Add default_language_version"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-27-pre-commit-template-update-mypy.rst:18
msgid ""
"Python のバージョンを明示することで、pre-commit が仮想環境構築時に意図しない Python バージョン（例: "
"3.13）を掴むのを防ぐ。"
msgstr ""
"By specifying the Python version, you can prevent pre-commit from grabbing "
"an unintended Python version (e.g. 3.13) when building a virtual "
"environment."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-27-pre-commit-template-update-mypy.rst:25
msgid "mypy の pre-commit フック対応"
msgstr "mypy pre-commit hook support"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-27-pre-commit-template-update-mypy.rst:27
msgid "型チェックを pre-commit に統合することで、ローカル／CI におけるチェックの一貫性を確保。"
msgstr ""
"Integrating type checking into pre-commit ensures consistent checking "
"locally/CI."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-27-pre-commit-template-update-mypy.rst:29
msgid "また、よく使われる `types-*` 系を `additional_dependencies` に指定している。"
msgstr ""
"Also, the commonly used `types-*` series is specified in "
"`additional_dependencies`."

